Biog._

=Guines, Modiste.= =Ch= Récollet, 115.

=Guise, Captain.= =D= His voyage to North-West Coast for sea-otter, 22.

=Gunn, Donald= (1797-1878). Born in Falkirk, Scotland. Entered the
