rear-admiral. Died in Paris. =Index=: =Hd= Mentioned in Haldimand's
correspondence, 245. =Bib.=: Sherbourne, _Life of Paul Jones_;
Mackenzie, _Life of Paul Jones_; Hamilton, _Life of Paul Jones_; _Cyc.
