Britannia_, 129; conference with George Brown on Confederation, 152,
154. =Bib.=: Works: _Nova Britannia_; _Canada and Her Resources_;
_Treaties of Canada_. For biog., _see_ Dent, _Can. Por._ and _Last Forty
